                            <comment id="12845565" author="jdcryans" created="Mon, 15 Mar 2010 22:22:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah I can also think of example client configurations. Currently it&apos;s really hard to decipher the text telling you to either put the quorum address or use the same hbase-site.xml from the cluster.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12845567" author="jdcryans" created="Mon, 15 Mar 2010 22:26:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oh and for the client, make a list of all configs that it really needs. Some defaults like the zookeper client port and hbase&apos;s parent directory (if you host more than 1 cluster per quorum).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
